{"word":"διαπορεύω","slug":"διαπορεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>διαπορεύω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>σω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to carry over, set across</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, with <a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>mid.</a> and aor1 <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> <el>διεπορεύθην</el>, <i>to pass across</i>, <el>ἐς Εὔβοιαν</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>: <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> cogn. <i>to go through</i>, <el>βίον</el> <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}